    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Knives with curved, spatulate blades, which may be in a half-moon or a crescent shape. These are used to cut heavy leathers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
